OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe US and Iran have signed an
OL,7,Fagreement calling for a permanent end
OL,8,Fto hostilities and kick-starting a 60-
OL,9,Fday negotiating clock between them.
OL,11,FThe deal, signed by US President
OL,12,FDonald Trump and Iranian President
OL,13,FMasoud Pezeshkian on Wednesday
OL,14,Fevening, calls for Tehran to dilute
OL,15,Fits stockpile of highly enriched
OL,16,Furanium and waives several US-backed
OL,17,Fsanctions on the country, immediately
OL,18,Fallowing Iran to sell its oil freely.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
