OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIt also opens the Strait of Hormuz
OL,7,Fwithout tolls for two months, but does
OL,8,Fnot preclude fees in the future,
OL,9,Faccording to details shared by both
OL,10,Fsides.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
