OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe document includes Lebanon in its
OL,7,Fopening paragraph, stating that the
OL,8,FUS, Iran and allies will declare an
OL,9,F"immediate and permanent" end of
OL,10,Fmilitary operations on "all fronts",
OL,11,Fincluding the country.
OL,13,FIranian Foreign Minister Abbas
OL,14,FAraghchi said on Tuesday that Israel's
OL,15,Fcontinued occupation of southern
OL,16,FLebanon would violate the deal, but a
OL,17,FUS official, who spoke on condition of
OL,18,Fanonymity, said it did not call for an
OL,19,FIsraeli withdrawal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
