OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe agreement takes "immediate effect"
OL,7,Fafter leaders from both countries
OL,8,Fsigned it, said Pakistani Prime
OL,9,FMinister Shehbaz Sharif, who helped
OL,10,Fmediate the agreement.
OL,12,FThe White House had planned a signing
OL,13,Fceremony on Friday in Switzerland, but
OL,14,Ffootage shared online showed US
OL,15,FPresident Donald Trump signing a paper
OL,16,Fcopy of the agreement at the Palace of
OL,17,FVersailles, just outside Paris, on
OL,18,FWednesday evening.
OL,26,@nD@UOUnD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
