PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIn the clip, Trump is seen seated at a
OL,7,Ftable next to French President
OL,8,FEmmanuel Macron and signs the paper
OL,9,Fbefore handing the pen to Secretary of
OL,10,FState Marco Rubio while people applaud.
OL,12,F"This was not easy," Trump said right
OL,13,Fbefore he signed it, adding later as
OL,14,Fhe left the dinner: "It's signed."
OL,16,FIn Tehran, a stone-faced President
OL,17,FMasoud Pezeshkian signed the deal on
OL,18,Fbehalf of Iran, according to the state-
OL,19,Frun IRNA news agency, which posted an
OL,20,Fimage of him holding up the deal with
OL,21,Fhis signature and Trump's.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@TO]vD@UOU
