CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe US agreement to immediately allow
OL,7,FIran to sell its oil freely and the
OL,8,Foffer to eventually lift all sanctions
OL,9,Fare major concessions that go beyond
OL,10,Fthe terms of Iran's 2015 nuclear deal
OL,11,Fwith world powers.
OL,13,FTrump withdrew America from that Obama-
OL,14,Fera pact in his first term, declaring
OL,15,Fit the "worst deal ever".
OL,17,FIt also calls for the International
OL,18,FAtomic Energy Agency (IAEA) to monitor
OL,19,Fthe "downblending" of Iran's uranium,
OL,20,Fwithout elaborating on what that means
OL,21,Fexactly.
OL,26,@wD@HOU{D@EOU{D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
