CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FIran maintains its nuclear program is
OL,7,Fpeaceful, though it is the only
OL,8,Fcountry to enrich uranium to 60%
OL,9,Fpurity without a weapons programme,
OL,10,Faccording to the IAEA.
OL,12,FThe initial deal provides a major win
OL,13,Ffor the global economy due to the
OL,14,Freopening of the Strait of Hormuz, the
OL,15,Fnarrow waterway through which a fifth
OL,16,Fof all traded oil and natural gas once
OL,17,Fpassed before the war began.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
