PN,30208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781765277
OL,3,CUS and Iran sign initial deal to end
OL,4,Cwar and reopen Strait of Hormuz
OL,6,FThe deal says the US will lift its
OL,7,Fblockade imposed on Iranian ports and
OL,8,Fthe strait will return to its prewar
OL,9,Ftraffic levels in 30 days, but
OL,10,Facknowledges Iranian mines may also
OL,11,Fneed to be destroyed.
OL,13,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,14,Four political experts are across all
OL,15,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,16,Fto the latest episode below...
